### JS Bundle Profile
```
Component             │ Size (gzip) │ Load Strategy
──────────────────────┼─────────────┼──────────────
LensToggle.svelte     │   0.95 KB   │ client:load
Quiz.svelte           │   2.60 KB   │ client:visible
Timeline.svelte       │   2.31 KB   │ client:visible
RatificationMap.svelte│  11.15 KB   │ client:visible
Svelte runtime        │   9.20 KB   │ shared
D3-geo + topojson     │   2.61 KB   │ dynamic import
──────────────────────┼─────────────┼──────────────
Total (max per page)  │  ~28 KB     │ progressive
```
